headline: Why Are Celsius (CELH) Shares Soaring Today
summary: Shares of energy drink company Celsius (NASDAQ:CELH) jumped 8.7% in the morning session after the company provided an upbeat business update at the Consumer Analyst Group of New York (CAGNY) conference, highlighting plans for growth and market expansion.
